呀 社服，罰錢&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;其他嘢<br />\n當然紅官依然要食屎"},{"pid":"e4e5bf14a2dbda908c6e4714a396af24b422b7ed","tid":2335913,"uid":306614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee1ce936503b6a4968d42820fa4f6ef6db54d092","tid":2335913,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c5642ac418517aad655d640f490a6f19ec40ba67","tid":2335913,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T08:24:25.000Z","msg":"DOJ 會否再上訴"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T08:31:02.000Z","msg":"認罪，有賠，仲想點"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T08:36:23.000Z","msg":"大波驊：黃絲全部要坐監！國安法！（設計對白）"},{"pid":"6e78e9f978c5527001e99dbff43cf7d3f3f56bd6","tid":2335913,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"51c3331af32d7434a1c05b4c68051dafa8cb81ec","tid":2335913,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"39462fb6e897461af60820812db4b240aca8e21b","tid":2335913,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T08:25:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T08:28:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T09:01:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4dc93767bde2f74958d67650a3b4f3ce9241cd6","tid":2335913,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T09:40:54.000Z","msg":"其後律政司要求改判拘禁式刑罰，溫官最終批准覆核刑期申請，但沒接納控方判監建議，只索取社會服務令報告。案件今再判刑，溫官指被告再犯機會低，且必定已對本案刻骨銘心，往後會謹慎行事，遂改判他接受200小時社服令，相信已具足夠阻嚇性及懲罰作用。<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201222/2ZUMCNCZKNGYBGVAX45EX7NKQQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201222%2F2ZUMCNCZKNGYBGVAX45EX7NKQQ%2F&d=YgirQyY3AADlg18%2F%2B2KZ%2FRZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=17f2f53e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201222%2F2ZUMCNCZKNGYBGVAX45EX7NKQQ%2F&h=a9dd0c6c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201222/2ZUMCNCZKNGYBGVAX45EX7NKQQ/</a>"},{"pid":"17caeb40ef37fa1ebaca6129a9ebef4ad3674ab5","tid":2335913,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T09:46:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1ab3669f97f0821077c12f24fb2466f83e51a2b","tid":2335913,"uid":226851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c5642ac418517aad655d640f490a6f19ec40ba67","tid":2335913,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T08:24:25.000Z","msg":"DOJ 會否再上訴"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T10:50:00.000Z","msg":"實會"},{"pid":"b007d51ea212bacecb422a4da164d23aa8885fff","tid":2335913,"uid":333752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T11:20:16.000Z","msg":"弱弱一問，刑期覆核唔係上訴庭做架嗎？"},{"pid":"fbda2e921f8bf5fcdf2148ca229c589391d3b5fe","tid":2335913,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b007d51ea212bacecb422a4da164d23aa8885fff","tid":2335913,"uid":333752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T11:20:16.000Z","msg":"弱弱一問，刑期覆核唔係上訴庭做架嗎？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T11:21:44.000Z","msg":"可以向原審裁判官申請,亦可以直接向上訴庭申請"},{"pid":"74cbaac6f82de3735ae10e000310820f7a7b7227","tid":2335913,"uid":1166